{"tid":1509701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"8月30日重光紀念日？","createTime":"2019-08-27T02:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:45:24.000Z","uid":188671,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c856083d2c454675d90d937131d4f2adbf2d16c1","tid":1509701,"uid":188671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"1946年，港英政府將8月30日定為「重光紀念日」並列入香港公眾假期，以紀念英國於1945年8月30日正式重新管治香港，並悼念在香港保衞戰為香港捐軀的將士。1968年，紀念日改定於8月第一個星期一及8月最後的星期一。1983年，紀念日改定於8月最後的星期一之前一個星期六、及8月最後的星期一。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人自發去和平紀念碑悼念？"},{"pid":"abc6e7dd9b3488a1f9b5736b4f7d0c3186d05dca","tid":1509701,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:33:11.000Z","msg":"呂麗乳搖呢"},{"pid":"fa0d852b95e461f3733f0a003414acc4de072fb9","tid":1509701,"uid":3419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:33:11.000Z","msg":"快過呂麗乳搖"},{"pid":"fb8f66aaa20cfb04ca581f7748f69524e9ea28aa","tid":1509701,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:33:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">612！721！811！你記得嗎？請香港人繼續走下去！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://im5.ezgif.com/tmp/ezgif-5-d5ebcebba7cd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fim5.ezgif.com%2Ftmp%2Fezgif-5-d5ebcebba7cd.gif&h=5f074275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">27/8(二) 動物界集會/遊行 轉場8.31民陣大遊行</span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhAWbhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhAWbhG.jpg&h=63a1860b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2wsp4CY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2wsp4CY.jpg&h=b919ba87&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">28/8(三) 圍堵國泰城 聲援航空界</span></span> <br /